{
  "stem": "26609.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to come at night time, and people were asleep, take the people-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all the people who arrived there who didn't have-- we had passports.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the Soviets, we used to have special passports that we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that we lived here before.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Other people couldn't obtain those passports.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "These had arrived from the other places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they were called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the Russians took them forcibly at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were screams on the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I remember at night time, the street screams.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'll tell you something about it later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They took them forcibly to Russia-- and everybody knew-- to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And no one wanted to go there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's why they hid there and around, and hid here and there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But they couldn't hide, because the Russians were everywhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they took them forcibly to Russia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were transported to-- to Russia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my mother could foresee what happens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When she came to Lwow to us from Grodek, she used to say, they don't know the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wish they would take me forcibly to Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That something worse will come, she could see it before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I believe that If they would take me and all my children, the whole family, I would go.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would ask them to take us too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they didn't take anyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took only the [NON-ENGLISH], those people from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
